                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:text="&quot;Do you keep hearing about ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE? What’s all the Fuss about it? Well this workshop is for you where you get started with basic concepts of ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE.&quot;"
